<!-- Menu — spec card render
     Source spec: ds-architect-agent/children/components/navigation.md#menu -->
<div class="dst-component-card">
  <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Menu</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">2 variants · 2 sizes · 4 states</p>
  </div>
  <p class="dst-component-intro">Floating list of actions, anchored to a trigger (icon-button, button, or text link). Distinct from select (which captures a value); menu invokes actions.</p>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Variants</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">default · bordered</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">ghost · floating</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Sizes</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">sm · 32px item</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">md · 40px item</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">States</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">closed</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">opening</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">open</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">closing</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-note"><strong>Item types:</strong> action (default, clickable) · separator · header (group label, non-interactive) · destructive (tinted error). <strong>Anchor:</strong> left-aligned by default; right-aligned if it would clip viewport.</div>
</div>
